These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, snowboarding, parkour
1. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
2. the person drinking tea is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person drinking soy-milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea   | fanta    | sprite    | soy-milk |
| Sport      | parkour | basketball | snowboarding | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, juice, water
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, tomato, papaya, blueberry
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
3. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person eating tomato##6
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola  | juice    | tea | water    |
| Food       | blueberry | tomato | papaya  | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, coffee, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, social-worker, manager, photographer
1. the person drinking lemonade is not the nurse##6
2. the social-worker is not the person drinking coffee##6
3. the manager is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the social-worker is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the social-worker##1
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the nurse is on the far left or far right##3
8. the manager is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | tea  | juice  | coffee |
| Job        | manager | photographer | social-worker | nurse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, dog, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the jet-ski is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rabbit | dog | bird     | turtle |
| Transport   | car     | motorbike    | scooter | jet-ski    |

