.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, mirinda, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, helicopter, bus
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
4. the person drinking water is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person driving the ship is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | soy-milk        | coffee | mirinda | water |
| Transport   | bus | ship | train     | helicopter   |

