.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie, satire, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, argentine, nigerian, pakistani
1. the dutch is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is not the argentine##6
3. the dutch is on the far right##1
4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
5. the person watching satire movies is the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
7. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
8. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
9. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | satire    | time-travel  | fantasy   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | pakistani | argentine | dutch |

