.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, animation, superhero, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, metal, punk, house
1. the fan punk is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
2. the fan punk is not the person watching animation movies##6
3. the person watching epic movies is the fan metal##1
4. the fan indie is on the left or right of the fan house##3
5. the fan punk is on the far left##1
6. the person watching animation movies is the fan indie##1
7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | animation     | superhero | epic |
| Music-Genre   | punk | indie | house      | metal         |

