.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, cola, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, librarian, analyst, writer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the writer is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5
3. the writer is on the right of the librarian##1
4. the librarian is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the librarian##3
6. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the writer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | water        | cola      | juice          |
| Job        | lawyer | librarian | writer | analyst |

