.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, software-developer, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, taxi, roller, bike
1. the designer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is not the paramedic##6
3. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person driving the bike is the software-developer##1
7. the designer is not the person driving the bike##6
8. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | designer  | software-developer | paramedic    | firefighter |
| Transport   | taxi | bike | roller | van  |

