.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, bird, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, rugby, ice-hockey, parkour
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the owner of the turtle##6
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the owner of the bird is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
6. the person who's sport is rugby is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
7. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | bird | turtle        | rat  | chinchilla     |
| Sport   | skateboarding     | parkour | rugby | ice-hockey |

