.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, reading, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, house, trance
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
3. the fan house is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is between the fan trance and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the fan folk is between the fan ambient and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | reading | singing    | dancing | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | ambient         | folk | trance   | house     |

