.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, watermelon, potato, eggplant
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, subway, car
1. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
2. the person eating eggplant is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
3. the person driving the boat is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person driving the subway is not the person eating eggplant##6
6. the person eating watermelon is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
7. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
8. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | lemon  | potato | watermelon | eggplant |
| Transport   | subway | jet-ski     | car     | boat    |

