.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, tomato, corn, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, fantasy, thriller, mystery
1. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
2. the person eating tomato is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person eating avocado is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
5. the person eating avocado is between the person eating tomato and the person watching zombie movies##2
6. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | radish | tomato      | avocado | corn   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | thriller | mystery   | zombie |

