.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, cola, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, zombie, animation, crime
1. the person watching animation movies is not the person drinking mirinda##6
2. the person watching animation movies is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person watching crime movies is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking milk##2
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | milk | almond-milk     | cola     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | animation       | crime | zombie |

