4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the photographer and the person who's sport is golf##2
6. the photographer is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
7. the dressmaker is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | coach  | videographer | dressmaker | photographer |
| Sport   | sailing | golf | soccer   | weightlifting |

