The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, helicopter, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the airplane is not the person drinking juice##6
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
6. the person driving the van is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice | hot-chocolate | cola      | 7up   |
| Transport   | tram  | van   | helicopter | airplane |

 